    "Be warned, though: if you accept my\n"
    "gift, the road ahead will be a\l"
    "perilous one.\l"
    "That is why I must test your ability\l"
    "in battle more than my Sisters.\p"
    "Are you ready to fight?"
}

text MtPyre_4F_Text_ISee {
    "I see.\n"
